WorkItem.Description:
Hey,
 
My Rawr is showing way lower dps than it should. It shows 3432 dps, when I get 5k+. I've set up the buffs so that it's just the ones I would have when I'm on a dummy, and I also retested my dps, I am above 5k. Can someone help me please?!
 
Thanks!
 
Rawr version: 2.3.8
Model: balance druid

Comments.Message:
Rawr thinks you'll be out of mana long before you finish a 5-minute fight on a target dummy.  Shorten the fight length, or give yourself some more mana or regen (self innervate, potion, BoW, ...).

You selected 100% Replenishment uptime, but no replenishment buff.
Ahh right, thanks! Yeh, now I put it down to 3 mins, it's showing about the dps I expected. Thanks again!
